high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the sink.
Pick up the mug from the inside of the sink.
Turn to the right and go to the microwave.
Place the mug in the microwave, run the microwave for two seconds, and take it back out.
Turn left to face the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the mug on the base of the coffee maker below the spout.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, then go right, then left behind the table, then turn right to go to the sink.
Pick up the mug from in the sink.
Turn around, then turn left and go to the stove.
Heat the mug in the microwave above the stove.
Turn left to go toward the dishwasher.
Place the mug at the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, head towards the oven, turn left towards the sink on your right.
Pick up the black cup inside the sink.
Turn right towards the oven, look up towards the microwave on above the oven.
Place the cup in the microwave, warm it up, take it back out.
Turn left to face the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm cup on the coffee maker.
